Facet Example -- Iris Dataset

p <- ggplot(data = iris, mapping = aes(x = Sepal.Length, y = Sepal.Width, color = Species))
p + geom_point() + facet_grid(Species ~ .)

Facet Example -- mtcars Dataset

p <- ggplot(data = mtcars, mapping = aes(x = hp, y = mpg, color = factor(gear)))
p + geom_point() + facet_grid(~vs)

Facet Example -- mtcars Dataset

p <- ggplot(data = mtcars, mapping = aes(x = factor(gear), y = mpg, color = factor(gear)))
p + geom_boxplot() + geom_jitter()+ facet_grid(~vs)
